{"tid":1393222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] UNSW連儂牆化身連儂站！展現BE WATER之最！","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:52:57.000Z","uid":247233,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c284d0a153c4b87dd1693291fd7c8d3155201751","tid":1393222,"uid":247233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"前幾日班學生自發性咁整左個連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cv4cJ00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCv4cJ00.png&h=f3973431&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZ1RZzm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZ1RZzm.png&h=461df078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就比隻大陸撕紙狗撕走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日同校方傾過之後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">校方批准學生表達訴求</span></span>同埋允許<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">擺街站！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以係呢度正式宣布，UNSW連儂站正式成立！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rnc2mTQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnc2mTQ.png&h=a7b245df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvT1Csb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvT1Csb.png&h=f29e679b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆主要都係比學校嘅人知道香港發生啲咩事同埋比人表達香港人嘅訴求</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">更何況UNSW主張言論自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n街站係逢星期四五10點到5點擺，所以希望身在悉尼嘅巴絲都可以貼爆佢！身在外地支持一下香港嘅義士！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請緊記be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撕一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df059cda46274d7ac06f4d19b9b5d62e0cb34245","tid":1393222,"uid":247233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8037f0af031f68b9ba3c4c39ded7413c93fcedd7","tid":1393222,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"cf3524c93cb192dfaacfc038ac5100e361f14b0d","tid":1393222,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國勢力"},{"pid":"68f65dcc68ec550333c137b2dbe4e8ec0df030cc","tid":1393222,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"睇左段clarification，想補充少少"},{"pid":"87df47391da12f9a7f51b7e4c00304238ac77e64","tid":1393222,"uid":247233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"19fb36e1a4e4155153c1c18e21d2203a457a1956","tid":1393222,"uid":18137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a844fb4de9af219cb58a88845d3b327fd27a0870","tid":1393222,"uid":296015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}